title: Nebula Line
summary: The Nebula Line is a line of massive haulers utilized by the Trade Union. They have unmatched cargo capacity, and can be used to make a lot of money.
full_text:
Nebula Line
The Nebula Line is a line of massive haulers utilized by the Trade Union. They have unmatched cargo capacity, and can be used to make a lot of money.

**The Andromeda is not a playable ship; instead, its model is used for the Trade Union freighter NPC's.
